source.name: 2009-2011 American Community Survey 3-Year PUMS Housing File
source.description: A nationwide survey that collects information such as type of housing unit, electricity cost, home value, monthly rent, vacancy status, and other data. Data from the American Community Survey and the Puerto Rico Community Survey were collected during calendar years 2009-2011.
